      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A criatura has a magic tome. Enquanto holding ou carrying the tome, a criatura can use its Banishing Garra action.\nThe tome has AC 17; HP 35; e Imunidade a Necrótico, Veneno, e dano psíquico. The tome recupera all its Pontos de Vida no fim de every turn, but it turns to dust se reduced to 0 Pontos de Vida ou when a criatura dies. Se the tome is destruída, a criatura can create a new one when it finishes a Short ou Long Rest.</p>",
          "chat": ""
